 serif;"&gt;当&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-s6WhKGFYEClMVhlf6FSPelBcSWx42nme87iAt0UEPl6EfMH30WRFF5VZmZP0hidw73JRIQKKsmjfNjz3oZw8ErfgOGDpUJvckSMQJhqRFNzlyhdufCg1qTfbDxi9I8b-riOJQhf-GGwqC2ry6ZqqaKidGxjl8WkEBAWmO1tZqsJBaebxNwtIa9Zui9q5C19aNeQWn_XITHG7of9L4D-7oWXcRJqprHUpc0dzcy__vGIzyuVhUXLPd-BxGV74z4KbO-JyWJ5XG0IMvNztpjcXNG7HWEGI6khk3rg7IBxOTvuceN_oIJvu1bCWS_NsBVTxbWUsoGQ0_BhohaFxohJTHpjjfcYn8-JQu1mayUOqdFEfpMVLpkMaq4-C9Q/wciDlAmZLdx0xlgCxMZAsfUGYfac_xNW/7" target="_blank"&gt;美元&lt;/a&gt;成为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AMC3h62eZPm74HacRdMw64_8GiIdNhEzY-2laCPYzAAxbmtKWvghz6YDRE7IKM5Dcl6U2973wDVwZJwkA-lB2fYS16pimiiNKgxwmsTSzazZPhZK-gG4s6bjK4hYITOVeVFBtPGQPlYFkjx-MQlTxrlpOtUArEIvj4yJCMb0U2p1pQfPjKl63bK6q4H6VJU5RbvAGC_57WIELuNEPnZq71KMdpgmZf_RwIoA28N_6cBpvVJUpvY5uQitHPE43d613m0cLSAa5Z-_PCHxKFLbR3Xx8ZnPDktx66GC97Bx57Trf4nHOI58P1iLSPI7aVYNfAMH6EKRNuzXH9mv2G9OhhSfcX6BFjw1T2QHjJN0BPgC3l0HQL8C83_qvQ0/fL21vNmQONJOdMkGakyg1NLK1xvzWuO5/7" target="_blank"&gt;市场&lt;/a&gt;中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pEGSCS-d2Jlik9XLym_6OTyi6HAcl0GdZU8VPjbozD7ovLr5plKDxioVA--zEdvktJE1eE4-9ajgmHPgoGhntdeWhzZHgYTdu3jp9oGT3WIzew6Bp5FfPZ4EoVJvvuxQLyC37GhQbC-iRPKqnxHERtyN7Pamcts390ltDO07AyJk3j3_qDm0cch4LobDpi2AZwm99Aj8UyF2PG7h3WTXSmIZg_n5gT0GabSZvAkDK6t-vaat5vQFMeMJmzdlSM9mrAQxH8pOXRzgEQKP5UCImODC8dmRiQGi3ETKLlOA-jCXhTZc710MQ_4o1Yc_Kn0sv_Wl4EKdn82L6px1ibnxPQdn8ZEInvi25Bf10jUAW5hwOoW1YEFlsFROOHA/-Oq7GLlw8sVhbJiMsZ5JzjioQ3CtcEor/7" target="_blank"&gt;动荡&lt;/a&gt;的受害者时，财政部长&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yBZSIvdgMi-dJGJ69k-TQ_OdsMwDEDvS9EyAo-NqFvQzC3l67TPvoMPtMSi70BFyMp-OgZYznR40-EHNQQfI69b5G1jHvvQtNQaVMdNM0y0S8nEJ7ezdDr14jNIyo_Q9OKBPq417IOWXr9TKrwqUd6UAdVbBy3bz3_3YGvfvj9wyq7pqbKqN2CtFwKbublBCzRnBbDYUFO5qc-HfOy0Cbaq-jGnVH3wNY27m9aVsyCDoDqpbmfT2PRR7dwrqivEgi76MjVM0g43r_Bvd75LnH_GQ7r_MVASgq81PB6UjtDumH4CSogMkGfWIdmagEz4wghQKV5Qz8UFH4XQlWuOmiumNN60Ps0RLrQe_Vked9JU9srVJg4fdWbXFS0w/XF1XRGg2m9KorXsVDMSl1a3ZT3juuZ4d/7" target="_blank"&gt;斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）&lt;/a&gt;领导着特朗普的顾问。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;英国在2月份的近一年中的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/i3wBt7T50Gy0ATwzSu5k0YcFzqEdbn4t_d40G9u0ABRa9KwrFS-GROm5BCPaVIWAfUUlhXVq7qnzzBQy4zyljuRO42XpPnguJ_73WiTEHre_juogXjSVAlL05OWWR-W6xV5fEidFEGVgXp7ZhG1ShVlCDpLdNgd0gDRV2rasuUgYnXwHHNgxaxFyLvR2Hv1DgnBesw5OEpwil8008ld91q7WPSlYOc8jwgh2D5STi3DIXf1dKy02_FEsoop04UG2KawBiOMT6VWeocvE-eK7pHCqtPk7RqyVy5_ANjuIagJqccP9s08ZUUZOcYWZwOf8AAkOfILnoR6iW6kblQiR-gxTXCvZS8wCudG6tp2o8cwq0I5Uzw-l_eT1OPc/Rn92HrYGTcZBFkbUVMvLA_SVRdSJDPfW/7" target="_blank"&gt;增长最强劲&lt;/a&gt;，工厂在特朗普的关税之前加大了生产。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;收入不足&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;如果美国是一家公开交易的公司，则可能需要发出相当于利润警告的等同，或者更准确地发出赤字警告。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;就像国会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VSOALiB2EJErCGbylGFUdo1UCFfWj-EmLAEd6S2JSkL3Rw3YoGSQE1iZs02fP_C8D4Z9JXIzGzcwSU100llbwlOijNzJwmgA-1EdnxL1lihwwcHxk9Tl2j7U84z8tmViE3vFI_YIJCZvP-t0DgYdIfv-ICggAE0OIGeBMPsBazwHML9mTn6dm2ApeanMFhpkUecAoqY-g3MhunrvgJlJ6Wh52RaRL1W2uPssKqpiHb3flXLNrK6YaNmxO72Uirqe1HTGgrgwFvwWTvwAigYYUtkY9yiiUuHu7wcc4fLlrmVf2JkbcfdnEjXD06v7rNCeR2mqr9tpwJ_TA_QaAo9hgyufJ_sGDieZ4yTWmi7I1tr_JA83f16hEr2ank4/Bag_3NnSEfjqdcbIBYLQkaW--qaMZQTz/7" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;越来越接近&lt;/a&gt;同意唐纳德·特朗普总统在竞选期间承诺的数万亿美元减税措施一样，在未来几年中，一些政府收入来源的预测要低于预期。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;到目前为止，最大的短缺是美国可以从关税中产生多少关税，特朗普和他的顾问指望的是帮助减税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;随着关税公告每天（如果不是小时）的限制，估计&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VQ8FCzVpibc2H_7nhsQWrpt51rM_FbMq9C0h-aKTp1EoNFBfkk_5qppvw1YD8cgw_GnjKo5ZKutl00MwCE2wCkW9nFqp4U7C8knDjJ0mQPiC4PGcbelzPO3ZVIc9MKaqTXUo1sjsxLXvFMMtwjuF2jltIO77uo22t_zprBEFviIPKCuYfXEPnGUTvLqy7zS4oUBJ_ULzMoFlfeC8q1rmGG6dcEy0YTqptFDrd5xMYDbvlgRGuRFsc51VufDRNk_ycN3vpxlBlNjTP2D5vDfO61_oPtH0nsLiOfO53NIvRaeZR2V9lzLMHqSWzAejWtkN8OkD-87yuptvd_5YR5QLNgJa4OINoywsuOP2OH0-Gz7oM32Q083fPCrhJWfXHj0DS_hqRoVmqal4FW6GcPIgczJVm3ur02-GZ9_TcyaPN72XpUHbCwsGoY6BZs6dgEQXwdTTW9JunE88WmDrGzuBtUZK8o55TbFSND0atpQWhfKvEpVM6ITJ8YRmD2zKtQ/dT9BJNVqL3zxcAcU-z7bqUjYcFVz8Dem/7" target="_blank" title="税收基金会"&gt;不断变化&lt;/a&gt;。但是总体预报员同意，关税&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2x4TmSl8Y4XYHel9wQp_zr45fJVZ9MIn5hoXx6dLW3prkVeET7aVh0X8oPDg_Zbimk4o_GBchTNYk-BGskmZK6W4dh9C3r4g7omN__2n7m23j-CxAjeCI7F0OgiHJLxYosx5rSfU7Ib1cL9y6FoknMahjjFy8Zaj6DUeVnUsmZrvpWbhr7FKLYvZGE9KLvOTC9UU0pSB21kdHcC3rdSwpPnINFzMoSZd-0vMg4NawbYW-89BwQJ4n4q9qaksx3MPDYZtCg70-vxr2iZOKWYZ5kAMAxxfRlSGzGuh45FgUeMY23negLeOWWOhF1yTJJ3oieP7e5GgD_qs7D3o19D6Hg8mI7SIgpWQYCdtZ-xspefmIN7izIcZa3h5uOg/G5U7H2Q8XCm_F8TO0wEobcABiZprdicA/7" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;的&lt;/a&gt;收入将少于每年的6000亿美元数字。这部分是因为关税可能会导致进口量下降。由于贸易战而降低消费者支出和商业活动也将最终减少税收的收入。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itpfgyKJNyDs/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itpfgyKJNyDs/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;特朗普政府对无证件工人的镇压可能较小但相当大的收入短缺。耶鲁大学预算实验室估计，国税局&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/JGL2kGDL0row0bseX7Yj4xNm1LdnD3Cjgfb6j9EAniQFkIONkAodKw0CANAyFRifOvRyjkWTFsyhPOBiO7jPfgng-cufjKX8E9aifYrCifU50o_oIYFBm-f5aWEr9I5JnaaOsyXndL4qIrLo1pGHJvDQc4HXMtl95xny0CctmEbDBd-T1NceERqNBRUjzt2cECor0zo_jKupXxAQXXa1QAXKszE4IFMuzO_0cZ0WqsRlJjTRwnx-KgbX0bWKGbY1HHaFTSgyNO0K_zzy53Z2eb8_8Oxm98OQlOoy9cnYyM3nA3aICoWpGQbva2Jqxq7hEHQr2ebKgGMCCUO_fgHF9cEkIFjzUjGxE7-1j_p-8balVbVvQ0b7XtnNeTA/LF9ghCCXmUTrEQl4eLDOdah-FXVd0mdz/7" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;在2026年的税收收款中可能会损失约260亿美元的税收&lt;/a&gt;，这是未来十年的3130亿美元 - 最近的一项交易使移民官员获得IRS税收数据的访问权限，以检查涉嫌非法在美国的纳税人的移民身份。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;该组织说，其估计有些不确定性。但是它认为，未经授权的移民在2023年缴纳了660亿美元的联邦税，大量来自工资税。现在，许多移民可能会三思而后行，或者在征收税收之前或在黑市上转移工作。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;上个月，当关税越来越大的时候，美国财政部在海关职责中看到了一个&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fsRWszI9HVITB5VG86xWXbelU4Q03L2X9vBA6DpvHfiKQyVwH1B8WJzxM-uWQJ3xgVDO3jOC7jo7Z16AgbOR_ZYkys2ihQFSYhtQGp1a5uu5ahGQQXDf46GbGa6B-My73cHDI-ft-4kj7FAzdJIw-y1MV63krXXMedkg8t44Yc6Y15GKAhHatB006FCXySULVUtteUuAOuOrmb3R0Pjj8VKpv8W0Pu_rRxqmr2G972vbhHxGWHAPvj5h5I0ipwOB7BhZmzLllqLZ-_zyD-oUMgrDfsxgnYpt3zEfWXE-ZV9QCIJZvpci5PdqdSgL8VGqXuOOok80CCHYlv1_6qpCkVEsZumIFrGq3sQY1ibREzvbZOC0Oe8xJ3B3HIA/FJXLcykNWCkWUMdmu58G7ywngPDtUUb3/7" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;适中的皮卡&lt;/a&gt;，尽管不足以使财政赤字扩大。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ro18bM1Ea8tZJut1rTe7NYD97UjGvN4yGk3ev311dCzl4A02wfzrUSOeBTgNFfBW0olEN56LCjC6koWgVVEhfpv4tcYe8N-fB6WnQmukshljmJeOKd-GliLhr_VMYHq7ipQ0F8kW_efJvNAldXexpG-dkL3Im6Ts-56P7DND--FVFvuf-GdLx9hZ0EhUIOcLvkqWwDntE1SqgyA6cW-tOVVkKwFwbtq0_FkzlC-3w0gkwWxwdND58fT0cg_ehy8tP5PI4kUYvtsmJpj6robjTXcrqTiEcJ2TP0DI4kYGMqryv1TFNSe9im5w8E3aHfFCO0oS73lSUr-KBdoW9tUArGX0rAEM7aS4-3HAdJrAqCwzttwFi0fOo2YkmMMmBiN9rF-n0B6J1m56sShToyMM6D3H4LPLFsO7DFc46cWY2CxkaIEQDk-Rgl0svVcAUrcr-hQPoSTrmmSqlYpovMQ7CzXBt5I0AEbzKe8wkmHiEMQAVcFWRn6BM6vq8Q1qdJOBOtYoukejUlMLaijx9iIsBo9srxlyli92b2qoJNfsrWul7cKfkuUVNaXFvMTGPJOspYPLnpun_rxxlwNrWEBg34