"0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;彭博经济学最好的&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;日本政府已经建立了一项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WSdY3piFiIy8QrY04Ny5_Ke75wKoAUkZ2bhiP0ASrKPv_SCfyIp9fhteO0b0dOhSQjP_Rv9LhI70oarfxBT6wNaVh5lSnzl7d2qPW7CccDHpkyNVvsoW4xMbLE9eOuhIl2WaY_hBktdD7wWf2B6t4Kazvv1aaqVmBzhVjpQlchGTuV1S9fXvc_pm2aoOwD_f9zw5jAl8_oXbpMTsniUCc14KacztIfeSCHCt4PSab9LKqvs68jWHTL0srQ6RGCHgUiKqcnte3Tjt3rtneVwfZWNw5xDwjb4TkD1QQtFSpB2j9w0fes0A16RUcwxrmjv3OmLovmISAqA1R8Y2TGv-tMvKkqgjjVmHCpLHJG7REWvobRLCsHJKpVjxmOw/YOz1HB01tQxZ9xC4t8iv1i7Nt5g0Tc9Z/7" target="_blank"&gt;关税工作组&lt;/a&gt;，而越南在华盛顿举行了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RftJDXUmio1XuaX87y6ww0_YTASDlvuB14opkbgxbBlgH1OT9XgNF_vETkPyuHiuoWE1T9JYnJIqGU7vfYkeI7rQ6M7fuqO2-oXEib42dxJwW0suQavoR-G5csCF-1ZGpwprKdm-8J7Kk2Szeq_AF2WE4fCMRHMDwgetNwNWc-uwrLcN4NhIyHuQnJBVCyvdU21whsr6p7yFLKtKVKFdi-y390MSiERQ56erwh8VzVxJm1IgDfT9chq1v8wKj2ZagOSSoItg2NjKHGa2PBmms9MKVYTvATo7NrhUNEcCuDw3_JiDw4wEgth64HqVCCjU0fwhV3cK7w-fuuS1qU4bcjuZBQE6B7ZwUdU-6TxjyP6QKEjeU7QMx_ZCJb8/4LUwy-Ww7S8yaEAQsWw7A0rOdVMEx88z/7" target="_blank"&gt;贸易会谈&lt;/a&gt;，墨西哥正在研究&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Qm9kmR5UpiLXka2ex9Nu0p5JC8gAPU6835kV67V5UA-7jmQRsLfTkNL-6T6IIW58qF2phbhXyCJR4M8V3IN-fvq6A8xemhMmWLDtJKMbr1Ie0qjwl_SfWjLO91sCo4OU5I6iB5IbKvcGLCwPYHDkTHwg64SeDxjCoB7Np1v8XfQfy7n9KazBfTT3shjtn5V_i6wp3B38tm2wF7FUtodmhtwvyPEA_A3QiK4nlrc3IAMyTYRfpY-hp75ODR5QmzgKQDDWGI67Dnr1Rxlq69YWsYV-9kXbnWk7eiKIj_7a6jmY9kTqVLLlHT2hnVdDVTBnD1ovX2jvBdKfyUvlBW7BTQ2D7ecUSBROsIIQMdiOft8UlG9P66a7eAaEEkY/kma1vvh00sFvqGruu9v1uNU_0ZPzX0Vw/7" target="_blank"&gt;汽车豁免&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;美容，头发和个人护理人员一直在亲眼目睹美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/CJUNySJdEV1bfDlS0IBI8ufNMZyaW0pTve0kh1FsuwfzAdBksD3nQwnaWTXMA