&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/tozdO1hgbNuBtZSWbwg3iZuk8QdF4tlLMtI3ncj5ZShnvhJ6xh7cjEl7Tv-1B-p8wMnG8v75PzgR0OBPc0q6f7C2VgKxG99hamVq_k2fO_kRngzPz8JK9oiFDiAmKuMxNbHN8gMBzRUVJwaLGz8u57FKyctz8SCXdrPUDkEaSxMv-FU4elsagjqhG4_io3y9lHScBr6a8I9nAyKDscZsnIOam79bQIITJqM7CFMvmsq5Hs3QbsiQM6iBv8VoTvMlkBcNoRq15ntNS2foFL6neda2rvbrOh7DJu1jNmqeMOiUA-d9OffPrynl7mT8slV3sfRUmxlaL4kBEb0pssl0uY7YAMIaZRKx6MIYvK88XlQ03gVIeefJU4zRmUc/EAVgxCeJKDp6n-RaWfQaIT1W5eD6E0AN/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDCYuWVfmFsQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDCYuWVfmFsQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Victor J. Blue/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普总统&lt;/strong&gt;在美国制造iPhone的梦想正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bVrP3SQXQlEkEv3kMMCzb1hBY1xefhdyiIbRjq4xG7N111EcIMBKpfiZhYDeW7p6gVtwpMZBw2sTCdJdYpg-bQcUw_dcPgdghmFytlei5i6euQ0z_lqPVAw0BvbEkXxZyeJ2tZlnM1R-cW1HaFd1v70J7uthw7Jc1V0mZSAJFQE3wKVE6LIOIq_x14m3OHbjf4B6lo7qiHahUvfIjl_azM2uDRLLFcU_cfEioe2e2r9XfvQuBSKTbJa2nkY-EKnBmLlOrl3pjaIoXIntestBzwxMwfrS5FOBe7vrPpfwWFpFvGLfFyJYREnIBc25wxeD-dpBRvXf1N9b7bOevdX4neMTtWoDvRW3R_8tH0UJA_iBoquo6Ha6MDPdH_c/-AxW6MIPacYRACxh6niesArLxJFlBh43/7" target="_blank"&gt;抗击经济学的艰难现实。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;苹果不太可能&lt;/strong&gt;在可预见的将来转移产量，原因有几个原因包括设施和劳动力短缺。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;此外，&lt;/strong&gt;美国缺乏丰富的供应商，制造和工程专有技术的生态系统，目前只能在亚洲找到。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;近年来一直保持一致的&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;事情&lt;/strong&gt;：美国的iPhone价格。但是，特朗普的关税政权增加了消费者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eSxm4j_c9zKSBIulqw6ltdsiNXVPrN1cRCuYhABwbUiTqjmp-obovRSTGwDuxc5DsxEiVVGWspHzBFD5eM1fHuwA647F4MWxuv016cPR9uMWimkvfcA_gX-5zsuplC9CyM9RHuIkVQs5Q4yl7-Ngk3hnrvYi1VReNUIiz2o0GR7munajuTKymN-TwqRQykQq2GAO6U2K_DL74J83DzKyfH4CmV46hc9Kxr3FL-943xg-UBQfMFXRJEX2kCGZ7iYcfFrHYVaLMOA4we7JSYmnaE-0GiqsxUOYBxYcz46EOqDvjR6XarQzMkzBeZNIqkzOJs_EzhYCfhYb1gv2Umy3o7MiI-EIWfZnU1FrNSg5f67neVe2J3me8Ah7a6c/nYpwIoyuPdVRi-Z4Yp_hk2RBRhDZfKrY/7" target="_blank"&gt;必须支付更多的可能性。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;在过去一周中，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;很少&lt;/strong&gt;有人可以期待。但是， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3rYpj3vWDaurluspguqfNIbH4zOLTP4VNTWHBujanL4jCUrPcZqXz4lMullSYwHgcZ_v_NogSueBm2-86MWXJDRzxTEssF0WyBXuBN2g4O6XkqHNqZK8hN5oAwJFgpnbJaVLnUaZgMnVvze97NR4xKjtzJN1eQ5gQy04rsNyU7c9JGwxpk3I2JZ_dMPmP0eGNgTTIdMNc2GJqdC1_ungLJFXTwRG3-0GbNal80-SgFDQuLnepBI51V8YHm3OXZKdUX4mn6cZSnijZCx124IJ14Ko3bumHEiYC7ySkJKH28zs_Wxw1VRw0vEt58inFVRI9PB-xWWmiFpPkhAIhzqbErJscydkcBVadjYzh53T64PHOGXAL0admqhXlkk/FS-2xcKozONRwv278ma6eDBkyjPVJ-Jj/7" target="_blank"&gt;来自印度的iPhone（从字面上看）&lt;/a&gt;可能位居榜首。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;要&lt;/strong&gt;对特朗普强加的“互惠”征税以及为什么， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vGuLLtD_S7YaIAH0tfMaXmNwGC_0rOHrZIPou__NSgrgMGJjxPpjcFbYKuUKm9Iw1GcJGB6A0OwJ02pPnwDEnNkcAFxXSH-u9exs3VlFvlh7Jt8UZflIEjoFlS8qTIRXP1ZsoYqZ1MVcwm3ecmfSnlR9Fdi9hcy8QaU1_90g5xfg05GMFXk5Quvo5ZoSbD1AFo0o_ob3xpz_nXmwuVAr7kptdh-TNTUzih_U4zkLcBongh2ns_F0yXHtx0FZNrMVo9yw99cokBvGFZbn6emQTaB_STK-_SBClwTuyY50L7IYtoKo8kAWC0nuQ0XR24-juJlplA8m_EsHWfDssnFbAJCvsIlv4Ohjhz_HX-QAHHmyhXPcsMSdBV1Xu6s/G4jWClZzFvbjLg47C9oyJxaL0tDQ5Tct/7" target="_blank"&gt;请看一下我们的解释器。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SyWHRrp2I6H7ZeagiCKzqzal5njTTtWwDSbU-whLphrm9UUhwNqoFN3TrBKZ3J-7rlUJg14hBd61TZtEWMOYyzmKhSJOR9NO10ivNupw5jte0EVmMh0yxArKLQmD_c621e06gElJkFz1WYJCIp1npqwCBdF4gq5sWiB12KhOgt1RTq0q2vSgw9Bo610gMiUhIS5x6b1abbEljEpNlLxdEt8vbykrnDSxaMNsbO-MtnpdlgZZXz5f3vryGTry3wuU9p83S3J-LDfdLkYJ48O-b7R_pnG6mPoJCACGSjNBwtUkUHoTtW_VQqO0EZcVzUnB8R7EPmIetgCI9-5zyJB8ZRbxeeJ8Yp6np57yZzljJ0ryLVQRlPZaS8tgHis/wTNnD24qj4wTYEyv6QItWOfZK5vfAc-3/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPj_UGcO9TLE/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPj_UGcO9TLE/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p styl